headline: My 3 Favorite Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stocks to Buy Now
summary: Ares Capital is a giant business development company that offers an eye-popping dividend yield.  W.P. Carey is a REIT that offers a yield above 5%, and it raises its payout every quarter.  Realty Income offers a yield above 5% and monthly payments.
